          <p class="first-para">Subject to Parliamentary approval of any necessary Supplementary Estimate, the Office for National Statistics DEL will be increased by &#x00A3;3,863,000 from &#x00A3;141,651,000 to &#x00A3;145,514,000 and the administration
          <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_13ws' title='Col. 13WS &mdash; HC Deb 27 November 2003 vol 415 c13WS' name='column_13ws' href='#column_13ws' rel='bookmark'>13WS</a>
